OL,3,CVolunteer lifeboat captain retires
OL,4,Cafter 51 years
OL,6,FAn Isle of Man RNLI volunteer who has
OL,7,Fsaved 13 lives and answered more than
OL,8,F300 calls is stepping down from his
OL,9,Frole after more than half a century.
OL,11,FJames Michael Keggen MBE, known as
OL,12,FMike, is the Isle of Man's longest
OL,13,Fserving lifeboat crew member after
OL,14,Fserving at Port St Mary Lifeboat
OL,15,FStation for 51 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
