OL,6,FMike who is a Funeral Director by
OL,7,Fprofession, has undertaken a wide
OL,8,Frange of roles including crew,
OL,9,Fmechanic, helm and coxswain, serving
OL,10,Fon both the station's all-weather and
OL,11,Finshore lifeboats.
OL,13,FOver the years Mike has been called
OL,14,Fout more than 300 times, aided at
OL,15,Fleast 124 people and saved the lives
OL,16,Fof 13 individuals.
OL,18,FAt the start of this year, Mike was
OL,19,Fmade a Member of the Order of the
OL,20,FBritish Empire (MBE) in the King's New
OL,21,FYear Honours.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
