OL,6,FUpon reflecting on his long service to
OL,7,Fthe RNLI and the official recognition
OL,8,Fhe's received, Mike said: "It has been
OL,9,Fa real honour to receive the
OL,10,Frecognition in my final year of
OL,11,Fservice, in the same year that the
OL,12,Fcharity celebrates 200 years of
OL,13,Flifesaving.
OL,15,F"The RNLI was founded here on the Isle
OL,16,Fof Man, and everyone who volunteers
OL,17,Ffor this special charity are all
OL,18,Fworking together as one crew, to save
OL,19,Flives at sea.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
