OL,6,F"We don't give up our time and energy
OL,7,Fto get recognition, we do it because
OL,8,Fwe want to serve our communities and
OL,9,Fkeep people safe."
OL,11,FMike inspired his children to
OL,12,Fvolunteer at the RNLI. His daughter
OL,13,Fand fellow volunteer Sarah Kneen said:
OL,14,F"He's given so much to the station and
OL,15,FRNLI - and to think of him dedicating
OL,16,Fover 50 years to lifesaving makes us
OL,17,Fall so proud."
OL,19,FMike remembers helping numerous
OL,20,Fpeople, but describes some of the more
OL,21,Fmemorable incidents
