OL,6,FOne rescue off the Carrick Beacon
OL,7,Finvolved three young people onboard a
OL,8,Fboat who had got into difficulty. No-
OL,9,Fone was wearing lifejackets and they
OL,10,Fhad no means of communication. Two of
OL,11,Fthem tried to swim to shore whilst the
OL,12,Fthird person stayed with the boat.
OL,14,FMike said: "The first swimmer managed
OL,15,Fto reach the shore and raise the alarm
OL,16,Ffor the lifeboat to be launched. We
OL,17,Fdid a detailed search in the all-
OL,18,Fweather lifeboat and managed to locate
OL,19,Fthe second swimmer who was in
OL,20,Fdifficulty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
