OL,6,FMike Teare, Port St Mary RNLI's
OL,7,Fcurrent Lifeboat Operations Manager,
OL,8,Freflected on Mike's contribution to
OL,9,Fthe charity: "Mike has been a stalwart
OL,10,Fof Port St Mary Lifeboat for as long
OL,11,Fas most can remember. He has served
OL,12,Four community as an RNLI volunteer for
OL,13,Fover 50 years ` an incredible feat.
OL,15,F"Whilst we wish him all the very best
OL,16,Fin his retirement ` his skill,
OL,17,Fknowledge, expertise and dedication
OL,18,Fwill be sorely missed. On behalf of
OL,19,Fthe crew, past and present, thank you
OL,20,Ffor your exceptional service.'
